          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1625593049526-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1625593049526-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms are crispy, add the <strong>spring onion batons</strong>, most of the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once done, transfer everything to a plate (save the pan!) and set aside until serving – these are your <strong>salt & pepper mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1625593090867-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1625593090867-x400.jpg",
