            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once combined, push the rice to one side of the pan and crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> onto the other side</p><p>Stir the<strong> egg[s]</strong> with a wooden spoon to break the yolk[s] and cook for 1-2 min until it resembles scrambled egg, then mix it all through the rice – this is your <strong>egg fried rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
